de.oaam.model.oaam.systems

Interface SystemsContainerA

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Subsystem, Systems
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SubsystemImpl, SystemsContainerAImpl, SystemsImpl

    public interface SystemsContainerA
extends OaamBaseElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Container A'. The systems model contains a high level description of the system components as well as the data and power flow without specifying the implementation.

    The following features are supported:

    • Systems
    • Information Flows
    • Input Segregations
    • Subsystems
    See Also:
    SystemsPackage.getSystemsContainerA()
